This C program is to make communication between processes.

I use two threads in this program, one is created within the terminal process.
And the other one is the terminal itself.

I also use two pipes to do the communication between the terminal and the shell.
http://www.csl.mtu.edu/cs4411.ck/www/NOTES/signal/kill.html
http://www.gnu.org/software/libc/manual/html_node/Signaling-Another-Process.html
The websites above is the resources that I refer to when I write my program.